    <string name="project_support_summary">Get the paid app to support future developments and extra features</string>
    <string name="project_support_description">
        <![CDATA[
        We believe privacy should be free. That\'s why all essential features are completely yours without spending a dime.<br>
        If you love what we\'re building, consider buying us a coffee. As a thank you, you\'ll get:<br> <b>All themes, Custom color, and Custom fonts.</b><br>
        This isn\'t a premium tier. It\'s a thank-you gesture. Your support keeps Rill independent, private, and ad-free.
        ]]>
    </string>
